ves</li><li>Full Size LED Ceiling Panel </li><li>Soft Close Large Pantry Drawer and Crisper</li><li>90 Degree opening hinge for True Flush Installation</li><li>Reversible Door</li><li>Holiday Mode</li><li>Eco Mode</li><li>Energy Star</li><li>Sabbath mode</li><li>*Internal Water Dispenser + Ice Maker on URBM36SIW Models</li></ul><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Spill Proof Glass Shelves</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Make cleanup easy by containing spills and preventing them from leaking down.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Full Size LED Ceiling Panel</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">White LED ceiling interior illuminates the interior with bright white light.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Soft Close\\u00a0</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Convenient soft closing drawers are quiet and gentle, providing a high end design.\\u00a0</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Reversible Door</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Allows you to choose between right or left swing for installation flexibility.\\u00a0\\u00a0</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Soft Close Large Pantry Drawer and Crisper</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">The soft close drawers offer the optimal storage for fruits and veggies in the crisper, while the pantry drawer allows you to pick the\\u00a0 temperature setting best suited for storing deli, cheese, wine, meat or cheese.\\u00a0</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Energy Star</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Meets specific efficiency standard to show efficient energy usage which means cost saving and is more environmental friendly.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bott