a-hidden=\\\"true\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\">         <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"product-desc\\\"><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>ILVE\\u00a019.8 cu. ft. Built-In Bottom Freezer Refrigerator</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">ILVE\\u2019s built-in refrigerators are designed and built to last while providing the best experience in food preservation. Choose between panel ready to match your kitchen cabinetry or with ILVE colors and handles to harmonize together with the kitchen suite. It is further covered with a 2 year warranty to provide you with a peace of mind.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><ul style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><li>14.2 Cu Ft Refrigerator Capacity / 5.6\\u00a0Cu. Ft Freezer Capacity</li><li>Adjustable Spill Proof Cantilever Glass Shelves</li><li>Full Size LED Ceiling Panel </li><li>Soft Close Large Pantry Drawer and Crisper</li><li>90 Degree opening hinge for True Flush Installation</li><li>Reversible Door</li><li>Holiday Mode</li><li>Eco Mode</li><li>Energy Star</li><li>Sabbath mode</li><li>*Internal Water Dispenser + Ice Maker on URBM36SIW Models</li></ul><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Spill Proof Glass Shelves</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Make cleanup easy by containing spills and preventing them from leaking down.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Full Size LED Ceiling Panel</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">White LED ceiling interior illuminates the interior with bright white light.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Soft Close\\u00a0</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Convenient soft closing drawers are quiet and gentle, providing a high end design.\\u00a0</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Reversible Door</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Allows you to choose between right or left swing for installation flexibility.\\u00a0\\u00a0</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Soft Close Large Pantry Drawer and Crisper</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">The soft close drawers offer the optimal storage for fruits and veggies in the crisper, while the pantry drawer allows you to pick the\\u00a0 temperature setting best suited for storing deli, cheese, wine, meat or cheese.\\u00a0</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Energy Star</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Meets specific efficiency standard to show efficient energy usage which means cost saving and is more environmental friendly.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Sabbath mode</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">When enabled, all lights, alarms and display panels will be switched off to conserve energy.</p></div>.<br><br><strong>Freight Charges May Apply</strong><br><br></div>      </div>      <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_accessories\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tab\\\" aria-controls=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_accessories\\\" data-slug=\\\"accessories\\\" role=\\\"tab\\\" aria-selected=\\\"false\\\" tabindex=\\\"-1\\\"> <span class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtext\\\">Accessories</span> </span></h3>      <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_accessories\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_accessories\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\">         <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\">                     </div>      </div>      <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_videos\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tab\\\" aria-controls=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_videos\\\" data-slug=\\\"videos\\\" role=\\\"tab\\\" aria-selected=\\\"false\\\" t